<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>NotesMedia</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container ">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6 mt-5 mb-5">
            <h1 class="mb-3"><span style="color: #ab3a6f;">About Us</span></h1>
          <p class="text-start fs-6">
            Welcome to NotesMedia! We are thrilled to have you here. At
            NotesMedia, we strive to create a comprehensive educational platform
            that caters to students' diverse learning needs. Our mission is to
            provide high-quality study materials, notes, and resources designed
            to empower learners at every stage of their academic journey.
            Whether you are preparing for exams, looking for reference
            materials, or seeking to expand your knowledge, we have a wealth of
            content to support you.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our dedicated team of educators and subject matter experts curates
            and continuously updates our resources to ensure that you receive
            the most relevant and effective study aids. We believe that learning
            should be engaging and accessible to all, which is why we focus on
            creating user-friendly materials that cater to different learning
            styles. From detailed notes to interactive quizzes, our offerings
            are designed to enhance your understanding and retention of complex
            subjects.
          </p>
          <p>
            Thank you for visiting NotesMedia! Your curiosity and commitment to
            learning inspire us. We are here to support you in achieving your
            educational goals and to make your learning experience enjoyable and
            fulfilling. We invite you to explore our resources, join our
            community, and discover the joy of learning with us. Together, let's
            unlock your potential and pave the way for your success!
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 mx-70">
            <img src="/media/Banner.jpg" style="height: 700px; width:600px" alt="NotesMedia Photo" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
